#################
###### OVH ######
#################

IMAPAccount ovh
Host ssl0.ovh.net
User thibault@thb.lt
AuthMechs LOGIN
PassCmd "gopass show ssl0.ovh.net"
SSLType IMAPS

ImapStore ovh-remote
Account ovh

MaildirStore ovh-local
Path ~/.Mail/OVH/
Inbox ~/.Mail/OVH/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel ovh
Master :ovh-remote:
Slave :ovh-local:
Patterns * % !Drafts
Create Both
SyncState *
Sync All
Expunge Slave

